description: Starts a data source connector synchronization job. If a synchronization job is already in progress, Amazon Q Business returns a ConflictException.

parameters.name: dataSourceId
parameters.description: The identifier of the data source connector.

parameters.name: applicationId
parameters.description: The identifier of Amazon Q Business application the data source is connected to.

parameters.name: indexId
parameters.description: The identifier of the index used with the data source connector.

nested_items.name: executionId
nested_items.description: The identifier for a particular synchronization job.
